{"tid":1774334,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍美松苑未補價首破「六球」！","createTime":"2019-12-08T07:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T10:05:53.000Z","uid":267488,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4b798343b7c9ce2881b63289c1c974b47fc9ea0b","tid":1774334,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"近月樓市走勢大起大落，部分二線居屋樓價表現更是飄忽。世紀21奇豐區域經理李仕明透露，大圍居屋美松苑F座樂松閣高層4室，實用面積645方呎，原圖則3房戶，望山景，原業主以650萬元放盤4個月，終減至未補地價626萬元成交，樓價仍屬該居屋未補地價首度衝上「六球」關，呎價9705元。<br />\n<br />\n高層3房戶呎造9705元<br />\n<br />\n原業主1996年以未補地價146.44萬元購入，賬面獲利479.56萬元，升值3.3倍。<br />\n<br />\n好飄忽地GOGOGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6edc1b6b887f60b667d6ffdb6aa8fc18441559","tid":1774334,"uid":114487,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"未上車就盡量黨鐵 狗封左好多過海隧道附近ge行車線<br />\n<br />\n多你一個人多好多 即刻出黎"},{"pid":"39935a95aac4117ff5a847c5abded372686a4582","tid":1774334,"uid":135957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9025ce3a2a81c532d814b9604c2d0d2ba19678de","tid":1774334,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"39935a95aac4117ff5a847c5abded372686a4582","tid":1774334,"uid":135957,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T08:03:02.000Z","msg":"明年應該上千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d90fd62754687d6db2793d340ea56324d304fe6","tid":1774334,"uid":125688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"加油！樓主唱好俾我出貨"},{"pid":"704a276e7facfb6deb6f625408c70f83b4abc6c1","tid":1774334,"uid":128761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"399