plants, some of which are just coming into bloom. Orchids can be cultivated in vases or flower pots. In summer, the meadow is blanketed with beautiful summer flowers. In spring the meadow is a mass of lovely spring flowers. In the autumn, pretty autumn flowers bloom in the meadow. In winter, the meadow is covered in beautiful winter flowers. It's an extraordinary garden. Every valentine's day her husband buys her a bouquet of red roses and hydrangea. They're pretty cut flowers. His new table and chairs are covered by plastic sheeting. By the way, did you know that seventy one percent of the earth's surface is covered by water? Forty percent of the mars' surface is covered with carbon dioxide while ten percent of it is covered by carbon monoxide."},{"pid":"3ca06b85ea48a0ceafaad9ef32f91bb872b722d7","tid":1774334,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"On99<br />\n<br />\n有綠表都買唔撚起啦"},{"pid":"6cd7ffd870c201d238d2fb419765749bbfad5862","tid":1774334,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"又話樓市跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ffdc06ee6c7ab7a9fe8313222a0293962a52ea","tid":1774334,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"平ar"},{"pid":"8e5da002bc463e41918d614799ac90113d0fe7fa","tid":1774334,"uid":213007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7cac783bf16711720518162fe9e437e06ae7164","tid":1774334,"uid":221051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5ffcd2f46c5c7ee2489358fe3363fad9330ea609","tid":1774334,"uid":97314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"AA黎講你都做得幾明顯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"樓主唔似aa wor，反而似早幾個月高位入左貨的小業主， 想透過唱好托得幾多得幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:05:53.000Z","msg":"鎖3年 托得一時托唔到一世"}]}